{"tid":2368430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：歡迎WhatsApp推遲接受新條款期限 冀公司能充分解說 釋除公眾疑慮","createTime":"2021-01-16T07:31:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T08:05:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"228d0f7a9010c12da402a19b775a821c79a7c5b6","tid":2368430,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:31:27.000Z","msg":"私隱專員歡迎WhatsApp推遲接受新條款期限<br />\n<br />\n通訊軟件WhatsApp宣布推遲用戶必須接受更新私隱條款的期限。私隱專員公署表示，歡迎有關安排，讓用戶有充足時間了解新條款及私隱政策，以及作出考慮。<br />\n<br />\n專員呼籲該軟件在這段時間，進一步向受影響用戶提供更多資訊及充分解說，釋除公眾疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n用戶原本要在下月8日前接受條款，否則帳戶將會被停用，新期限是5月15日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570757-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570757-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyHXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=0158f7fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570757-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fd7d662f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570757-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7c1244ae7247e551324b911b4cac76260021b5aa","tid":2368430,"uid":90601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"充分解說 依句野好似邊度聽過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7932608caae6b1568214ed8d95849d5ab817ae4","tid":2368430,"uid":249866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:33:58.000Z","msg":"推遲到幾時都唔會再用WhatsApp。"},{"pid":"fabeb1faba28e09568512b3f1697370a3a6436b4","tid":2368430,"uid":12599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T07:34:57.000Z","msg":"歡迎暫緩，不用撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src